INCLUDE globals.ink

It's a cool dresser.
+ [Open] -> open
+ [Leave] -> nopen

== open ==
You open the drawers to reveal an array of hats objectively nicer than your own.
+ [Leave] -> leave1

== leave1 ==
The drawers close with a satisfying magnetic click.
-> DONE

== nopen ==
You decide you have some respect for people's privacy.
-> DONE